{"id":821,"date":"2016-12-29T13:09:01","date_gmt":"2016-12-29T12:09:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/?p=821"},"modified":"2017-01-11T17:45:38","modified_gmt":"2017-01-11T16:45:38","slug":"new-works-concept-entre-design-art","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/new-works-concept-entre-design-art\/","title":{"rendered":"New Works, un concept entre design et art"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>A la fronti\u00e8re entre ombre et lumi\u00e8re, entre design et art, le travail de New Works rend hommage \u00e0 la tradition artisanale des pays scandinaves en d\u00e9fiant avec audace les formes contemporaines d&rsquo;aujourd&rsquo;hui.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-826\" src=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10127_st\u00c3\u00b8rre_Final-708x1080.jpg\" alt=\"new-work-lejlighed10127_sta%cc%83%c2%b8rre_final\" width=\"708\" height=\"1080\" \/><\/p>\n<p>A l&rsquo;origine, c&rsquo;est bien la fascination pour les formes sculpturales et les mat\u00e9riaux bruts qui a guid\u00e9 les cr\u00e9ateurs du projet. Le concept de la marque danoise est fond\u00e9 sur 4 valeurs essentielles: respect des propri\u00e9t\u00e9s premi\u00e8res des mat\u00e9riaux (cuir, bois, m\u00e9tal, b\u00e9ton, marbre..), art brut, d\u00e9marche exp\u00e9rimentale cultivant le souci du d\u00e9tail, valorisation des processus artisanaux.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-825\" src=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10053_Final-706x1080.jpg\" alt=\"new-work-lejlighed10053_final\" width=\"706\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10053_Final.jpg 706w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10053_Final-471x720.jpg 471w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10053_Final-105x160.jpg 105w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10053_Final-314x480.jpg 314w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-822\" src=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/AURA_003_300-719x1080.jpg\" alt=\"aura_003_300\" width=\"719\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/AURA_003_300.jpg 719w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/AURA_003_300-479x720.jpg 479w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/AURA_003_300-107x160.jpg 107w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/AURA_003_300-320x480.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>L&rsquo;univers de la marque est d\u00e9pouill\u00e9 au premier regard mais la simplicit\u00e9 des formes est r\u00e9chauff\u00e9e par l&rsquo;utilisation de mati\u00e8res nobles et sensuelles comme le ch\u00eane, le cuir, le velour ou le satin.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-824\" src=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10036_Final-701x1080.jpg\" alt=\"new-work-lejlighed10036_final\" width=\"701\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10036_Final.jpg 701w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10036_Final-467x720.jpg 467w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10036_Final-104x160.jpg 104w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/New-Work-Lejlighed10036_Final-312x480.jpg 312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-823\" src=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/MATERIAL_PENDANT_GROUP-774x1080.jpg\" alt=\"material_pendant_group\" width=\"774\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/MATERIAL_PENDANT_GROUP.jpg 774w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/MATERIAL_PENDANT_GROUP-516x720.jpg 516w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/MATERIAL_PENDANT_GROUP-768x1072.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/MATERIAL_PENDANT_GROUP-115x160.jpg 115w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/MATERIAL_PENDANT_GROUP-344x480.jpg 344w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ils s&rsquo;appellent New Works, Suivez leur histoire.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-828\" src=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/NW_IMAGE_HANG_ON_HONEY_002_HUSK_BAGGRUND-770x1080.jpg\" alt=\"nw_image_hang_on_honey_002_husk_baggrund\" width=\"770\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/NW_IMAGE_HANG_ON_HONEY_002_HUSK_BAGGRUND.jpg 770w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/NW_IMAGE_HANG_ON_HONEY_002_HUSK_BAGGRUND-513x720.jpg 513w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/NW_IMAGE_HANG_ON_HONEY_002_HUSK_BAGGRUND-768x1077.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/NW_IMAGE_HANG_ON_HONEY_002_HUSK_BAGGRUND-114x160.jpg 114w, https:\/\/www.melville-design.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/NW_IMAGE_HANG_ON_HONEY_002_HUSK_BAGGRUND-342x480.jpg 342w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A la fronti\u00e8re entre ombre et lumi\u00e8re, entre design et art, le travail de New Works rend hommage \u00e0 la [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featur